       <strong>
        skirejser

       <strong>

    {{#author}}
         <div class="tt-socialstream-stream-header tt-clearfix">
             <a class="tt-target-blank" href="{{url}}">
                 <img class="tt-socialstream-stream-header-image" src="{{image.url}}" alt="{{displayName}}" />
                 <span class="tt-socialstream-stream-header-name">{{displayName}}</span>
                 <div class="g-follow" data-annotation="bubble" data-height="20" data-href="{{url}}" data-rel="publisher"></div>
             </a>
         </div>
         {{/author}}
         <div class="tt-socialstream-stream">
             {{#items}}
             <div class="tt-socialstream-stream-item">
                 <a class="tt-socialstream-stream-item-image tt-target-blank" href="{{actor.url}}">
                     <img src="{{actor.image.url}}" alt="{{actordisplayName}}" />
                 </a>
                 <a class="tt-socialstream-stream-item-title tt-target-blank" href="{{actor.url}}">
                     {{actor.displayName}}
                 </a>
                 <div class="tt-socialstream-stream-item-text">
                     {{&object.content}}
                 </div>
 
                 {{#object.attachments}}
                     {{#object.attachments.isPhoto}}
                     <div class="tt-socialstream-stream-item-photo tt-target-blank tt-clearfix" data-href="{{object.attachments.url}}">
                         <img src="{{object.attachments.fullImage.url}}" alt="Photo" />
                     </div>
                     {{/object.attachments.isPhoto}}
                     {{#object.attachments.isAlbum}}
                     <div class="tt-socialstream-stream-item-photo tt-target-blank tt-clearfix" data-href="{{object.attachments.url}}">
                         <img src="{{object.attachments.thumbnails.0.image.url}}" alt="Album" />
                     </div>
                     {{/object.attachments.isAlbum}}
                 {{/object.attachments}}
             </div>
             {{/items}}
         </div>
